==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nonmigratory
<hw>nonmigratory</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not participating
in migrations; -- used of animals that do not migrate. Opposite of
<ant>migratory</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> resident.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>living in one area throughout the year; -- used of
animals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nonmodern</ent>⟦br⟧
